EXPLANATION:

@intent("UI_ROOT")
- Tells runtime this is a UI application.

mut win
- Creates a mutable window object.

ui.create(...)
- Creates a window with title, size, and background color.

while (win : is_open)
- Main render loop, runs while window is open.

ui.rect(...)
- Draws a rectangle on screen:
  - pos = position
  - size = dimensions
  - color = fill color

